<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:13:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国参议院委员会批准可能限制中国生物技术的法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-senate-committee-approves-bill-that-could-restrict-chinese-biotech-2024-03-06/</link><description>美国参议院国土安全委员会周三投票通过一项法案，该法案可能以国家安全为由限制与华大基因和药明康德等中国生物科技公司的业务往来。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 15:03:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-senate-committee-approves-bill-that-could-restrict-chinese-biotech-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>荷兰部长表示欧洲需要快速、集中的科技产业政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/europe-needs-fast-focused-tech-industry-policy-dutch-minister-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>荷兰经济事务部长周三在接受采访时表示，在中美贸易紧张局势中，欧洲需要快速、有选择性和积极地支持关键科技行业。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:36:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/europe-needs-fast-focused-tech-industry-policy-dutch-minister-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>Antfin 通过大宗交易出售印度 Zomato 约 2% 的股份</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/antfin-sells-about-2-stake-indias-zomato-via-bulk-deals-2024-03-06/</link><description>证券交易所数据显示，中国蚂蚁金服周三通过大宗交易出售了印度食品配送平台 Zomato 2.1% 的股份。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 14:36:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/antfin-sells-about-2-stake-indias-zomato-via-bulk-deals-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>高级官员称西藏去年“没有发生重大群体性政治事件”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-serious-mass-political-incidents-tibet-last-year-says-senior-official-2024-03-06/</link><description>周三，一名西藏高级官员在中国年度两会期间的一次吹风会上表示，去年喜马拉雅地区没有发生“群体性事件”（这是抗议的委婉说法）。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:12:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-serious-mass-political-incidents-tibet-last-year-says-senior-official-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国为Stellantis-Leapmotor合资企业开绿灯--消息人士</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gives-green-light-stellantis-leapmotor-joint-venture-sources-2024-03-06/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，拟议的合资企业已获得中国监管机构的批准，该合资企业将允许世界第四大汽车制造商 Stellantis 在中国境外生产和销售零跑汽车的电动汽车。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-gives-green-light-stellantis-leapmotor-joint-venture-sources-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>世界市场为特朗普可能重返白宫做好准备</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-trump-graphic-2024-03-06/</link><description>在“超级星期二”确认唐纳德·特朗普将在 11 月美国大选中与现任总统乔·拜登对决后，投资者正在为唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫的可能性做好准备。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 13:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-trump-graphic-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>倍耐力预计 2025 年收入和利润增长有限</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/pirelli-says-operating-profit-rose-25-last-year-shares-erase-gains-2024-03-06/</link><description>意大利倍耐力周三表示，在地缘政治紧张局势加剧、通胀和高利率导致增长放缓和需求疲软等不稳定环境下，预计明年收入增长将难以超过 5%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:24:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/pirelli-says-operating-profit-rose-25-last-year-shares-erase-gains-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>前欧盟反垄断负责人警告国家龙头企业面临的危险</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/former-eu-antitrust-chief-warns-dangers-national-champions-2024-03-06/</link><description>欧盟前反垄断主管马里奥·蒙蒂周三警告说，创建国家龙头企业来帮助欧洲企业与中国和其他地方的竞争对手竞争可能会面临其他国家的抵制，并削弱竞争执法者的权力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 12:16:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/former-eu-antitrust-chief-warns-dangers-national-champions-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>美国参议院委员会审议针对中国华大基因、药明康德的法案</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-senate-committee-takes-up-bill-targeting-chinas-bgi-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-06/</link><description>美国参议院以国家安全为由限制与中国华大基因、药明康德和其他生物科技公司开展业务的法案将于周三在国会面临首次重大考验。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 11:07:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-senate-committee-takes-up-bill-targeting-chinas-bgi-wuxi-apptec-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔在大盘分散后开盘</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-06/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 11:03:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国抱怨荷兰有关台湾的新闻报道</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-complains-about-dutch-news-report-taiwan-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国周三对荷兰公共广播公司 NOS 对台湾的一则新闻报道表示不满，这表明北京对台湾的立场变得更强硬。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-complains-about-dutch-news-report-taiwan-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>京东季度收入超出预期，大幅折扣提振需求</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-e-commerce-firm-jdcom-beats-fourth-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-03-06/</link><description>京东(JD.com)，周三在美国盘前交易中股价上涨12%，此前这家中国在线零售商公布的第四季度营收高于预期，并宣布将扩大股票回购计划的规模。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 10:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-e-commerce-firm-jdcom-beats-fourth-quarter-revenue-estimates-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>西门子高管表示，随着经济繁荣，西门子对印度寄予厚望</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/siemens-has-high-hopes-india-economy-booms-executive-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>西门子董事会成员马蒂亚斯·雷贝利乌斯(Matthias Rebellius)表示，西门子对其在印度的前景“非常乐观”，因为该国经济蓬勃发展，并提供了摆脱中国业务多元化的机会。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 09:04:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/siemens-has-high-hopes-india-economy-booms-executive-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，摩根士丹利因市场暴跌而削减了9%的中国基金部门员工</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cuts-9-china-fund-unit-staff-amid-market-rout-sources-say-2024-03-06/</link><description>两位直接了解情况的人士表示，摩根士丹利已解雇其在中国的资产管理业务部门约 9% 的员工，因为中国不断上涨的股市削弱了其 3.8 万亿美元基金部门的前景。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:03:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/morgan-stanley-cuts-9-china-fund-unit-staff-amid-market-rout-sources-say-2024-03-06/</guid></item><item><title>国家规划师称中国2024年5%的增长目标可实现</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-step-up-economic-policy-adjustments-2024-state-planner-says-2024-03-06/</link><description>中国国家规划负责人周三表示，中国政府今年5%的经济增长目标是可以实现的，许多分析人士认为这个目标雄心勃勃，他预计世界第二大经济体第一季度将有良好表现。</description><pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 08:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-step-up-economic-policy-adjustments-2024-state-planner-says-2024-03-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>